<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="28Oct1937"><font color="red">28 October 1937</font> <i>NLHW</i> (from Harriet Weaver to Paul L&eacute;on): The correcting of proofs of <i>W.i.P.</i> must be an exacting task needing great care and concentration &hellip; I am glad to hear that the work on Parts I and III is nearly finished and that Mr Joyce hopes to be able to send the greater part of Part II to the printers early next month. </div>
